<body>
<div type="letter">
  
  
  <pb facs="1063235" n="1"/>
<opener><salute><lb/>Illustrissimo <abbr>celeberrimoq.</abbr> Viro
    <lb/>Nicolao Bernoullio <abbr>Math.</abbr> <abbr>Profes.</abbr> <abbr>Patav.</abbr></salute>
  <lb/>Sebastianus Checotius <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></opener>
<p><lb/>Ut affici condimentis quibusdam solemus, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fami non eximend<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
  <lb/>magis, quam excitand<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> acuend<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que primis mensis inferri solent, ita me
  <lb/>tuis <rs type="letter">Litteris</rs> affectum scito Vir Clarissime; quibus degustatis, cave exple<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tam putes cupiditatem tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> suavissim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> consuetudinis, quin ad eam potius
  <lb/>omni officiorum genere colendam novo <add>me</add> eoque acriori studio esse inflamma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tum; illis enim effecisti, ut, cuius antea doctrinam mihi <del>[...]</del><add>c</add>um ex erudi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tissimis <rs type="biblio">scriptis</rs> tuis, tum ex doctorum Virorum, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119112450">Hermanni</rs> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipu<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> at<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>que <rs type="person">Poleni</rs> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dicatione perspect<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>, demirabar, eius quoque singularis huma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nitas <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> candor animi summus, tot tantisque benignitatis in me ipsum tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
  <lb/>signis ne a me diutius ignoraretur. Itaque efficiamus, obsecro, mi Bernoulli,
  <lb/>ut quando meum ist<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> animum p<choice><orig><g ref="#oe">œ</g></orig><reg>oe</reg></choice>nit<choice><orig><g ref="#uacut">ú</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>s exploratum habes, conciliatam
  <lb/>amicitiam, quam fore sempiternam auguror, foveamus usque, tueamur,
  <lb/>amplificemus; tecumque exisitimes, me, ut eorum qui a te amantur c<choice><orig><g ref="#oe">œ</g></orig><reg>oe</reg></choice>teris
  <lb/>rebus omnibus fortasse imparem, in officio cert<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> referendo, tuisque eximiis
  <lb/>virtutibus colendis <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> observandis nemini concessurum.</p>
  <p><lb/><rs type="biblio">Dissertatiunculam</rs> me<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> Tomo Diarii 23<hi rend="sup">o</hi> insertam quod laudas, gratias ha<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>beo maximas; quamquam enim <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> tui similibus doceri malim qu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> laudari,
    <lb/>si qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tamen meorum ab huiusmodi probari video, tum vero mihi ipsi
    <lb/>incipio minus aliquantul<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> displicere. Pronunciatum de ill<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> tuum, quo
    <lb/>nempe nomine appellari malles, nunc demum intelligo ex ea, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> scribis,
    <lb/>Homonymia ortum habuisse; cur ego aliunde fluxisse crederem id <add>in</add> caus<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>
    <lb/>fuit, quod observaveram, nomen illi a me solutionis imposit<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> ide<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> tibi
    <lb/>minus apt<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> convenire visum, quod eiusdem qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stionis ex demonstrato
    <lb/>per te ipsum Theoremate elicitam solutionem pro rect<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> haberi posse
    <lb/>investigationis methodo pernegares: ind<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> fact<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> est, ut illi non absi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>milem investigationem meam te putasse arbitrarer, neque enim li<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cebat idnign<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> virtute tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quidquam coniectari, e<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>que te propte<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> suspicione liberandum duxerim. Eandem ego <rs type="biblio">dissertationem</rs>
    <lb/><rs type="place">Venetias</rs> vix curaveram Tomo 21<hi rend="sup">o</hi> inserendam, cum ab <rs type="person">amico</rs> 
    <pb facs="1063237" n="2"/>
    <lb/>certior sum factus locum illi nullum esse reliquum, <rs type="biblio">libro</rs> proelis
    <lb/>prope diem emersuro; <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> quid pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tere<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> a <rs type="person">Collectoribus</rs> <rs type="biblio">Articulo XI</rs>
    <lb/>eiusdem operis esset adnotatum. Quo viso indolui, mihi crede, rem
    <lb/>a <rs type="person">Viro Doctissimo</rs> in medio positam tam crud<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>, <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> veluti contemptu
    <lb/>quodam pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teriri, mihique intere<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> gavisus sum, quod in e<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> iudicior<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
    <lb/>iniquitate unus essem extiturus, qui rectius aliquant<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> sentire videri
    <lb/>possem. Cur ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> <rs type="biblio">Schediasma</rs> me<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> neque ab eo proximus vigesimus-<lb break="no"/>secundus, sed alter demum <rs type="biblio">diarii</rs> Tomus attulerit, ignotum mihi,
    <lb/>ni fort<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> id <rs type="person">Collectores</rs> cavendum pataverunt, n<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>, <rs type="biblio">scripto</rs> meo <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dito,
    <lb/>non sibi satis, et iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ante<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> dixerant constare viderentur.
    <lb/>Quos ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice>, scribis, de tuo in illa qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stione proponenda animo perper<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
    <lb/>indicasse, ni fidem dictis faciant, non video quo pacto apud <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quos
    <lb/>cordatosque viros purgari qu<del>[...]</del><add>e</add>ant, ut id proptere<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> si postulas,
    <lb/>tuo mihi jure agere videaris. Nunc autem, quod ad postrem<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vestigationis me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> perficiend<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> methodum requirebas, ut assumpt<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
    <lb/>figurarum <formula>ABG</formula>, <formula>abG</formula> similitudinem demonstrarem, non erit <choice><orig>|</orig><reg>(</reg></choice>puto<choice><orig>|</orig><reg>)</reg></choice>
    <lb/>ut a te amplius desideretur, ubi adverteris non postulari a me
    <lb/>illam, sed duobus prioribus <rs type="biblio">Solutionis</rs> Articulis statui atque
    <lb/>firmari, vim enim omnem <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> cardinem nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs type="biblio">solutionis</rs> e<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> loci
    <lb/>non obscur<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> deprehendes. Pervides porr<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice>, pro tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mentis acu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mine<supplied>,</supplied> Vir Clarissime<supplied>,</supplied> rectas <formula>AB</formula>, <formula>AC</formula> Coordinatasque coeteras
    <lb/>in Curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <formula>ABC</formula> non tempora aut vires esse, sed ad ista expri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>menda relatione quadam assumptas, si earum qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>libet cum
    <lb/>reliquis eiusdem generis conferatur; quo fit in re nostra, ut
    <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cumque demum absolut<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> temporum, viriumque signifi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
    <pb facs="1063238" n="3"/><lb break="no"/>cationes iis affingantur (analoga quad<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> substitutione) e<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dem ips<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> line<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>,
    <lb/>mod<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> semel rem confecerint, semper sint proposito satisfactur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>. Qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>quidem non peculiaria nostro, sed quibuscumque dem<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Problematib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice>
    <lb/>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unia <del>[...]</del><add>eru</add>nt, si quidem ad huscemodi constructionum norm<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> illo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum conditiones exprimi qu<del>[...]</del><add>e</add>ant. Quare nihil est ex hoc capite
    <lb/>quod me impediat quin, te annuente, aditione illius <rs type="letter">epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> iterum
    <lb/>observantiam studiumque in te meum public<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> testat<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> faciam.</p>
<p><lb/>Sed de his fortasse plus satis. <rs type="biblio">Solutionem</rs> tuam si mihi c<choice><orig><g ref="#oe">œ</g></orig><reg>oe</reg></choice>terisque
  <lb/>Matheseos cultoribus impertieris, rem gratissim<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> facies. </p> <closer>Vale
    <lb/>Vir Clarissime, <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> glori<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que ac sublimioribus istis disci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>plinis, quibus illustrandis es natus, perge consulere, mihique
    <lb/>fave, <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>, ut facis<supplied>,</supplied> ama.
    <lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs type="place">Vicenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>A. d.</abbr> <date when="1719-03-10">VI Idus Martias 1719</date></dateline></closer>
  <note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><foreign xml:lang="ger"><abbr>Empf.</abbr> den</foreign> <date when="1719-03-11">11.<hi rend="sup">ten</hi> Marti<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></date>.</note>
  <pb facs="1063239" n="4" type="empty"/>
</div>
